{"tid":1802590,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【黃色經濟圈】葵廣做黃色經濟圈嘅基地掂唔掂？","createTime":"2019-12-29T14:48:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T15:13:17.000Z","uid":73980,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a3758b3182564c1bc5fdcc25ab3d63ef2cc8ccae","tid":1802590,"uid":73980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T14:48:33.000Z","msg":"成個商場都黃到仆街。<br />\n<br />\n1.食店<br />\n<br />\n好多黃到爆嘅店，又會捐錢又有連儂牆，排隊多人到仆晒街。相反地下間藍田拍曬烏蠅，等執咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.服裝<br />\n<br />\n有啲賣衫嘅成日播國家，可惜得女裝咁做，暫時未見男裝店咁做。<br />\n<br />\n3.商場<br />\n<br />\n商場畀埋個位啲人貼連儂牆，畀晒面香港人。<br />\n<br />\n4.後生為主<br />\n<br />\n大部分都後生都係黃，而葵廣就以後生為主。"},{"pid":"5c2bdc52daf4697fe4b07787db823da6a638aa7a","tid":1802590,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T14:49:20.000Z","msg":"問咗天水圍新北江未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c4cc2f52337eb7b6503624a468157d77e61b683","tid":1802590,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T14:49:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國聯署有三份  呢家仲有一份未達標 <span style=\"color: red;\">最後兩日</span><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=OJrKX0dn%2BAqYJaSYBqJK94MY%2BwsNvTr2Nz54cwdIBJg%3D&h=7b5eb408\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"bb8ba730a7480f150ba86a477dc801fb7ea5aa0b","tid":1802590,"uid":325840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T14:49:52.000Z","msg":"好驚俾狗咬而慢慢變返港豬嘅唔該入一入嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800681</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"45fa4052cd0e851e8eef80dd400176b28b38e6bb